  "type": "mcq",
  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The function <span class=\"italic\">S</span> above models the annual salary, in dollars, of an employee <span class=\"italic\">n</span> years after starting a job, where <span class=\"italic\">a</span> is a constant. If the employee&rsquo;s salary increases by 4% each year, what is the value of <span class=\"italic\">a </span>?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph \">0.04</p>\n"
